            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-03/file7kbdbd4y7rn1fv8l7mbr.jpg?VersionId=gunjVl5QZg6LSve_GR6q_AY2pJzWZD3R&amp;itok=yFcRAPZo" title="第二十架接返自乌克兰撤离中国公民临时航班安全抵达福州。（新华社）" alt="第二十架接返自乌克兰撤离中国公民临时航班安全抵达福州。（新华社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-03/file7kbdbd4y7rn1fv8l7mbr.jpg?VersionId=gunjVl5QZg6LSve_GR6q_AY2pJzWZD3R&amp;itok=yFcRAPZo" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
